1
00:00:00,724 --> 00:00:03,593
How was the exam, Richard?
考试考得怎样,Richard?

2
00:00:03,799 --> 00:00:05,863
Not too bad.
不算太坏,

3
00:00:06,233 --> 00:00:11,059
I think I passed in English and Mathematics.
我想我的英语和数学及格了.

4
00:00:11,094 --> 00:00:14,012
The questions were very easy.
题目很容易.

5
00:00:14,013 --> 00:00:16,948
How about you, Gary?
Gary,你怎么样?

6
00:00:18,061 --> 00:00:24,019
The English and Maths papers weren't easy enough for me.
英语和数学试题对我来说不很容易.

7
00:00:24,020 --> 00:00:26,748
I hope I haven't failed.
我希望我别不及格.

8
00:00:26,749 --> 00:00:30,374
I think I failed the French paper.
我想我的法语及不了格,

9
00:00:30,518 --> 00:00:34,618
I could answer sixteen of the questions.
我能回答其中的16道题.

10
00:00:34,619 --> 00:00:36,989
They were very easy.
这些题很容易.

11
00:00:36,990 --> 00:00:40,013
But I couldn't answer the rest.
但我回答不出其余的题.

12
00:00:40,014 --> 00:00:43,459
They were too difficult for me.
那些题对我来说太难了.

13
00:00:43,577 --> 00:00:47,199
French tests are awful, aren't they?
法语太可怕了,你说呢?

14
00:00:47,687 --> 00:00:49,712
I hate them.
我讨厌法语.

15
00:00:49,724 --> 00:00:53,365
I'm sure I've got a low mark.
我的法语成绩肯定很低.

16
00:00:53,404 --> 00:00:55,738
Oh, cheer up!
啊,别灰心!

17
00:00:55,739 --> 00:00:59,403
perhaps we didn't do too badly.
或许我们考得还不太糟.

18
00:00:59,872 --> 00:01:05,499
The guy next to me Wrote his name at the top of the paper.
坐在我旁边的那个人在试卷顶端写了自己的名字.

19
00:01:05,758 --> 00:01:07,179
Yes?
是吗?

20
00:01:07,511 --> 00:01:12,410
Then he sat there and looked at it for three hours!
然后他坐在那里,对着考卷看了3个小时,

21
00:01:12,411 --> 00:01:15,002
He didn't write a word!
一个字也没写!

